<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.172204>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Haematotrephus limnodromi n. sp. from the long­billed dowitcher, Limnodromus scolopaceus. 1. Ventral view of adult. 2. Composite drawing of anterior end showing placement of the genital pore and terminal genitalia, ventral view. 3. Composite drawing of female genitalia, dorsal view. Abbreviations: O, oötype; OV, Ovary; S, uterine seminal receptacle; U, uterus; V, Seminal vesicle. Scale bars: 1, 3,100 µm; 2, 630 µm; 3, 510 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/172204/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

